# The move command executed successfully, indicating I am now at the intermediate position.
# I will now attempt to move closer to the nearest stone patch again.

# Moving to another intermediate position that is closer to the stone patch.
next_intermediate_position = Position(-12.5, -12.5)  # A point that brings me closer to the stone patch.
move_to(next_intermediate_position)  # Move to this next intermediate position.
